      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 16 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>豫，利建侯行師。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Yu indicates that, (in the state which it implies), feudal princes may be set up, and the hosts put in motion, with advantage.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
