      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 16 六二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 16 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：介于石，不終日，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, shows one who is firm as a rock. (He sees a thing) without waiting till it has come to pass; with his firm correctness there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
