      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 16 六三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 16 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：盱豫，悔。遲有悔。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows one looking up (for favours), while he indulges the feeling of pleasure and satisfaction. If he would understand!--If he be late in doing so, there will indeed be occasion for repentance.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
