      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 16 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 16 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：由豫，大有得。勿疑。朋盍簪。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows him from whom the harmony and satisfaction come. Great is the success which he obtains. Let him not allow suspicions to enter his mind, and thus friends will gather around him.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
