      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 16 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：貞疾，恆不死。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth six, divided, shows one with a chronic complaint, but who lives on without dying.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
