      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 16 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六：冥豫，成有渝，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost six, divided, shows its subject with darkened mind devoted to the pleasure and satisfaction (of the time); but if he change his course even when (it may be considered as) completed, there will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
